{"tid":616769,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)越空狂龍 冒牌慈母 轟天復仇","createTime":"2018-04-04T12:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T17:52:56.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0cf5401dc720bf66845db189eca4b3f8738ca9ec","tid":616769,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=M%2BVLkElJh%2F0an4e%2F%2B3q%2BteargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=bd1784b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=M%2BVLkElJh%2F0an4e%2F%2B3q%2BteargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=2b28c928\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/05/Demolition_man.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F05%2FDemolition_man.jpg&h=123ae13d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/0/08/Let%27s_Be_Cops_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F0%2F08%2FLet%2527s_Be_Cops_poster.jpg&h=865e07f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bf/The_Heat_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbf%2FThe_Heat_poster.jpg&h=d675e178&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/47/Parker_2013_Movie_Poster.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F4%2F47%2FParker_2013_Movie_Poster.png&h=099e190a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1996年，洛城警局分隊長約翰‧史巴坦（史特龍飾）領導一個營救小組，要從暴力犯罪份子賽門‧菲尼斯（史耐普飾）救出人質。在掃瞄了營救區域確定沒有人質存在的跡象後，史巴坦攻入菲尼斯的巢穴並且抓住了他，但是菲尼斯引爆炸彈炸毀了大樓。隨後竟在瓦礫堆中找到了許多人質的屍體，於是洛城警局以害死人質的理由逮捕了史巴坦。根據「冷凍罪犯」條款，史巴坦與菲尼斯兩人被判處在冷凍監獄裡長期拘禁，並且在冷凍時期給予「康復技能」<br />\n<br />\n2.苦苦掙扎的電子遊戲設計師賈斯汀&middot;米勒（威爾斯飾）和無業游民、完蛋的校隊四分衛萊恩&middot;奧馬利（詹森飾）是一對好基友，兩人回想起他們曾做過的約定：如果到了三十歲還不能在洛杉磯「幹一票大的」，就搬回哥倫布老家。離開酒吧時，兩人的車子被滿面殺氣的艾爾巴尼亞人開SUV給撞了，撞車黨還威脅兩人不要想著報仇<br />\n<br />\n3.派克（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）是一名「盜亦有道」的搶匪，他只搶富人，而且作案絕不傷害善良百姓。一次參加了一個犯罪集團，他打算收手，結束綠林人生，卻慘遭黑喫黑，差點淪為波臣。身負重傷的派克打算報仇，也希望獲得鉅款，金盆洗手，派克四處尋找仇家，希望能拿回他應得的鈔票，卻在因緣際會下，遇上了一位美豔的失婚女房仲經理人萊絲麗（珍妮佛&middot;洛佩茲飾），在若有似無的情愫中，兩人開展合作。派克的計畫是：以其人之道，還治其人之身....<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=M%2BVLkElJh%2F0an4e%2F%2B3q%2BteargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=58c6c9bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=M%2BVLkElJh%2F0an4e%2F%2B3q%2BteargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=eeffb300\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45019789f9f813f2bc4173741a6c09ea98988e1","tid":616769,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset